    <p class="sub">Nevarro is a boutique studio with two arms: custom AI software for niche industries, and a research team publishing digital products for consumers.</p>
    <p class="supportline">For any queries, contact <a href="mailto:support@nevarrotech.com">support@nevarrotech.com</a></p>

