  <!-- WHAT WE DO -->
  <section id="work">
    <div class="sec-kicker">What we do</div>
    <h2>Two arms, one studio.</h2>
    <p class="sec-sub">An enterprise practice that builds custom AI software, and a research team that publishes digital products.</p>

    <!-- ENTERPRISE -->
    <div class="offer" id="enterprise">
      <span class="tag">Enterprise · Consulting</span>
      <h3>Boutique AI software for niche industries</h3>
      <p>We partner with smaller-scale enterprises in niche industries to design and build custom AI-enabled software — working iteratively on defined artifacts (workflows, tools, integrations, and internal products) on a pay-as-you-go basis. Engagements are intentionally small and focused: one team, one problem, working software every month.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Custom AI tools and internal products, built to your workflow</li>
        <li>Iterative monthly delivery against agreed artifacts</li>
        <li>Deployment, handover, and ongoing improvement</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="pricenote">Typical engagements run <strong>$500–$1,500 per month</strong> depending on the range of services. <span>Final pricing and configuration are agreed in writing before any billing begins.</span></div>
      <div class="cta"><a href="mailto:adithya@gmail.com?subject=Enterprise%20engagement%20enquiry">Enquire about an engagement →</a></div>
    </div>

    <!-- CONSUMER / RESEARCH -->
    <div class="offer consumer" id="research">
      <span class="tag">Consumer · Research Products</span>
      <h3>Digital products from our research team</h3>
      <p>Our research arm produces digital products sold directly to consumers — ebooks, research reports, digital audits, and custom-made reports for specific industries. Each product is delivered as a digital download.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Ebooks and industry research reports</li>
        <li>Digital audits and benchmark reports</li>
        <li>Custom-made reports built to order</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="pricenote">Products are priced <strong>₹500–₹5,000 per digital download</strong>. <span>Custom reports are quoted individually based on scope and configuration.</span></div>
      <div class="cta"><a href="mailto:support@nevarrotech.com?subject=Research%20product%20enquiry">Ask about our products →</a></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT -->
